?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] in hi=
s San Francisco office two years ago. He was right in the middle of everyth=
ing at the dawn of the AI Age, so I asked him what was exciting him the mos=
t, of all of the incredibly exciting AI things to be excited by.
=E2=80=9CBusiness Process Automation,=E2=80=9D Anton replied. =E2=80=9CHave=
 you read Softwar?=E2=80=9D
So I DM=E2=80=99ed Anton and asked him to answer a question that=E2=80=99s =
